# Card Layout Patterns

## Fixed Height Cards with Content Scaling

To keep cards within bounds with proper content scaling:

```tsx
// Fixed card height based on viewport
<div className="h-[calc(100vh-220px)] max-h-[700px] overflow-hidden">
  <div className="h-full flex flex-col p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8">
    {/* Content fills available space */}
    <div className="flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
      {/* Scrollable area if needed */}
      <div className="flex-shrink overflow-y-auto">
        {/* Long content */}
      </div>
    </div>
    {/* Fixed bottom elements */}
    <div className="mt-auto shrink-0">
      <Button />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Bottom-Aligned CTA and Icon Layout

For CTA (left) and icon (right) aligned to bottom:

```tsx
<div className="h-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
  {/* Left: Content column */}
  <div className="flex-1 flex flex-col">
    {/* Content... */}
    <div className="mt-auto">
      <Button />
    </div>
  </div>
  
  {/* Right: Icon aligned to bottom */}
  <div className="lg:w-[240px] flex items-end justify-center">
    <img className="animate-icon" />
  </div>
</div>
```

## Centered Card Container

```tsx
<div className="w-full flex flex-col items-center">
  <div className="w-full max-w-[1200px] bg-[#d6c68e] rounded-[24px]">
    {/* Card content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

## Key Classes

- `shrink-0` - Prevent element from shrinking
- `flex-shrink` or `flex-1` - Allow element to shrink/grow
- `overflow-hidden` on card, `overflow-y-auto` on scrollable content
- `mt-auto` - Push element to bottom of flex container
- `items-end` - Align flex children to bottom
